{"id":"concepts/scrappy-travel","title":"Scrappy travel","type":"concepts","html":"<h1>Scrappy travel</h1>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Stub. Yahir's recurring travel mode — minimum-budget, maximum-improvisation trips. Anchors include the <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"summaries/2021-03-14-orlando-trip\">Orlando 2021 trip</a>, <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"concepts/peru-prep-2021\">Peru 2021</a>, and the 2022 potential-trips list. Connected to <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"concepts/bridge-income-strategies\">bridge income strategies</a> and the broader <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"concepts/voluntary-adversity\">voluntary adversity</a> frame.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2>Source summaries</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"concepts/peru-prep-2021\">peru prep 2021</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"summaries/2022-06-30-potential-trips\">2022 06 30 potential trips</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"summaries/2021-03-14-orlando-trip\">2021 03 14 orlando trip</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/orlando-fl\">orlando fl</a></li>\n</ul>\n","related":[{"id":"concepts/bridge-income-strategies","label":"Bridge Income Strategies"},{"id":"summaries/2021-03-25-orlando-bus-routes-airport","label":"Orlando bus routes — airport / mall / Gatorland directions"},{"id":"summaries/2021-03-14-orlando-trip","label":"Orlando Trip — itinerary planning grid"},{"id":"entities/orlando-fl","label":"Orlando, FL"},{"id":"concepts/peru-prep-2021","label":"Peru-prep 2021"},{"id":"summaries/2022-06-30-potential-trips","label":"Potential Trips — Sept 2022 cheap-flights longlist"},{"id":"concepts/voluntary-adversity","label":"Voluntary Adversity"}]}
